						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in a grove of trees near the village.</p>						

						<p>This undated record in characters of <hi rend="italic">c.</hi> 17<hi rend="italic">th century</hi> records, the raising of a grove which was gifted to Tiṁmappanāyani by Timmānāyani, son of (name lost) at Kuvvaṁ; the donee was to enjoy the fruits of the grove. Kūvvaṁ was under the administration of the donor. </p>						

						</summary>
